<H4>    Local Leaders To Accompany Li on Tour </H4>

<F P=102> OW2904155694 Beijing XINHUA in English 1513 GMT 29 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> OW2904155694 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing XINHUA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


