BFN 

  [Text] Hohhot, April 29 (XINHUA) -- Chinese Premier Li 
Peng concluded his visit to Uzbekistan, Turkmenistan, 
Kyrgyzstan, Kazakhstan, and the State of Mongolia and arrived 
here this afternoon by special plane. 
  Those who arrived at the capital of the Inner Mongolia 
Autonomous Region with Li were Li's wife Zhu Lin, State 
